2026-05-15T21:55:58.6478447Z 21    <!--
2026-05-15T21:55:58.6478845Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-15T21:55:58.6479299Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-15T21:55:58.6479938Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
